QUESTION

Age must be at least 18.

Monthly income must be 2000 and above.

Credit score must be at least 600.

If there is a previous debt, the application will be rejected.


NOTES

Immutable data model (final fields)

Monetary data with BigDecimal

Clear business result with LoanDecision enum

Open to extension (for example, you can include rules in LoanEvaluator as a list, strategy pattern)

MIN_* values are defined as constants.
